# Praesidium .gitignore

# Rust build output
/target
**/target

# Test assets: staged kernels, built .pex images, QEMU firmware var copies, swtpm state,
# any downloaded/large boot artifacts. Sources for these live tracked under test/ (like Warden).
/test-assets
/tpm
OVMF_VARS*.fd
AAVMF_VARS*.fd
*.pex

# Local scratch / editor
*.swp
.DS_Store
/.idea
/.vscode

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Private planning docs (ACTIVE — mirrors the Warden privacy call).
# The repo is public, but the architecture docs and standing rulebook stay local-only:
# ADRs, specs, and build-specs (all under /docs) plus CLAUDE.md and TASKS.md are kept OUT
# of git so they never leave this machine. Claude Code still loads CLAUDE.md/TASKS.md from
# disk regardless of git tracking. Remove a line below to publish that file.
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
/docs
CLAUDE.md
TASKS.md
